    • Constructor Detail

      • IntelligenceTask

        protected IntelligenceTask(com.solvvy.mturk.TaskBuilder builder)
        Construct a new IntelligenceTask from a task builder.

        Due to the high number of arguments that need to be set for an IntelligenceTask, it is easier to use a fluent-builder style.

        Parameters:
        builder - a task builder that contains the arguments to be passed to the IntelligenceTask.

        public com.amazonaws.mturk.requester.HIT create()
        Creates a human intelligence task from the provided information and delivers it to mechanical turk to be answered. Also updates the Hit Id for each snippet in the database. If the task had already been created, it is simply returned instead.
        Returns:
        the created HIT
